## **💡 AI Agent Workflow Summary**
| **Step** | **Action** | **Command/Tool** | **Success Check** |
|----------|------------|------------------|-------------------|
| 1 | Create restore point | `Checkpoint-Computer` | Restore point exists |
| 2 | Download tools | `Invoke-WebRequest` | Files in `C:\OpenWin11` |
| 3 | Debloat Windows | Sycnex script | Bloatware removed |
| 4 | Disable telemetry | DisableWinTracking | Telemetry blocked |
| 5 | Disable updates | Group Policy/Registry | Updates disabled |
| 6 | Disable services | `sc stop`, `Set-Service` | Non-critical services disabled |
| 7 | Preserve critical services | `Start-Service` | NVIDIA/Wacom services running |
| 8 | Disable tasks | `Disable-ScheduledTask` | Tasks disabled |
| 9 | Enable Test Mode | `bcdedit /set testsigning on` | Test Mode watermark appears |
| 10 | Customize UI | Registry tweaks | Large text, no animations |
| 11 | Install package managers | Scoop/Winget | `winget list` works |
| 12 | Verify workflow | Manual test | All apps work |

